Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.50,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}球也轻飞扬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.05,0:22:05.32,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}看见后不禁驻足下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.89,0:22:08.88,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}为何不击出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:12.15,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}下一个球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:18.69,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}想一想真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:25.69,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}一分之差如此遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.29,0:22:28.96,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}你也是这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:38.37,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}站在打击区的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:42.13,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:46.41,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今后的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.70,0:22:53.82,ED2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是一段你变坚强的旅程
